{
  "name": "RPlog_Third_Battle_of_Mon_Calamari_-_Opening_Moves",
  "title": "Opening Moves Over Dac",
  "summary": "Marshal Krieg Inrokana leads Task Force Inquisitor out of hyperspace over Mon Calamari, claiming a humanitarian mission to supply the Quarren Survivalist Party while driving a wedge toward the planet to land ground forces. Admiral Ackbar's New Republic fleet refuses the ruse and opens fire, and a sprawling battle erupts: the corvette Audacity under Commander Rasi Cen -- with Chief of State Leia aboard relaying intelligence from a mysterious Sluissi contact -- duels the Imperial corvette Prowler, while Rear Admiral Quix coordinates the defense with hidden minefields and droid fireships. The Jedi spring their own trap: Luke Skywalker's cloaked cruiser Refrain of Anshalar (crewed by Seth Senesca and Ver-Tak Kai) decloaks to strike the Imperial rear, and the Sullustan apprentice Enb'Zik in Ranger One blinds the enemy sensor screen by destroying a scout to open a corridor for reinforcements. Pilots Anzon, Tarin, and the mercenary Kirkland trade blows with Imperial fighters as Krieg drives his force planetside under a torrent of QSP submersible torpedoes orchestrated from Aquarius by Korynn Fleming. The Imperials punch through the minefield and withdraw to the system's edge, leaving an uncertain Imperial presence on the surface -- round one of a far larger fight.",
